<head>BOTTOM</head>
    <list type="altnames">
<item>UNDERSIDE</item>
<item>UNDERNEATH</item>
<item>UNDERSURFACE</item>
    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">底部</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>PART of an ARTEFACT or THING that is MOST LOW.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current word for the bottom of a vessel is dǎng 當.</p>
<p>2. Dǐ 底 is a Han dynasty dialect word for the bottom of a vessel.</p>
        </div>
